<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Contact | Gemino AI × 3D Creative</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f8f9f1; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0;">

    <header style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #556b2f 0%, #2e3b10 100%); color: white; padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center;">
      <a href="/" style="color: white; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.8;">← Back to Home</a>
      <h1 style="margin: 20px 0 0; font-size: 2rem; letter-spacing: 2px;">CONTACT</h1>
      <p style="margin-top: 10px; opacity: 0.9;">ご依頼、アイデア、ご相談はこちらから</p>
    </header>

    <main style="max-width: 700px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 0 20px;">
      <div style="background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
        
        <form action="https://formspree.io/f/mdaaergn" method="POST"> <div style="margin-bottom: 25px;">
            <label style="display: block; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #2e3b10;">お名前</label>
            <input type="text" name="name" required style="width: 100%; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; box-sizing: border-box;" placeholder="姓名">
          </div>

          <div style="margin-bottom: 25px;">
            <label style="display: block; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #2e3b10;">メールアドレス</label>
            <input type="email" name="email" required style="width: 100%; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; box-sizing: border-box;" placeholder="example@mail.com">
          </div>

          <div style="margin-bottom: 25px;">
            <label style="display: block; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #2e3b10;">お問い合わせの種類</label>
            <select name="type" style="width: 100%; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; background: white; box-sizing: border-box;">
              <option value="order">3D制作・修理のご依頼</option>
              <option value="idea">制作アイデアの投稿</option>
              <option value="consulting">コンサルティング・仕事の相談</option>
              <option value="other">その他のお問い合わせ</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div style="margin-bottom: 25px;">
            <label style="display: block; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #2e3b10;">メッセージ内容</label>
            <textarea name="message" rows="6" required style="width: 100%; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; box-sizing: border-box;" placeholder="具体的なご要望や、ワクワクするアイデアをお聞かせください"></textarea>
          </div>

          <div style="text-align: center;">
            <button type="submit" style="background: #556b2f; color: white; border: none; padding: 15px 50px; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.1rem; cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.3s;">
              メッセージを送信する
            </button>
          </div>

        </form>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top: 40px; text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem;">
        <p>※通常3営業日以内にGeminoよりご返信いたします。</p>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer style="text-align: center; padding: 40px; color: #888;">
      <p>© 2026 Gemino's 3D & Info Blog</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
